</div><a class="XnPoMwM8" rel="nofollow" href="/fonts/pg-2" data-discover="true"><div class="GOuSMDop"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ sNjFhu89">2</div></div></a><a class="XnPoMwM8" rel="nofollow" href="/fonts/pg-3" data-discover="true"><div class="GOuSMDop"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ sNjFhu89">3</div></div></a><a class="XnPoMwM8" rel="nofollow" href="/fonts/pg-4" data-discover="true"><div class="GOuSMDop"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ sNjFhu89">4</div></div></a><a class="XnPoMwM8" rel="nofollow" href="/fonts/pg-5" data-discover="true"><div class="GOuSMDop"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ sNjFhu89">5</div></div></a><a class="XnPoMwM8" rel="nofollow" href="/fonts/pg-2" data-discover="true"><div class="GOuSMDop" data-testid="pagination-next"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ sNjFhu89"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" title="arrow right" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#chevron-right"></use></svg></div></div></a></div></nav></div></div><div class="ES35fwD6 Z8wCehge sNjFhu89 If79kg54 SHv85Oe2 GjgsucRA uedkJzta M7ikmWSE"><div data-testid="discovery-survey-rating"><div class="QejAgNG_ R7OCkfor rGep5HSU"><div class="QejAgNG_ R7OCkfor akbOyW7N"><span class="_7yoIykb4 LEo3ecOM oddFflBz Qu5eWXzk">How satisfied are you with your Fonts experience today?</span><div class="LTyNgPJu akbOyW7N J3nrzrT4 i7W3a7Tu"><button class="C7bQRdPs" type="button"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-secondary, currentColor)" title="Unrate 1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#star-outlined"></use></svg></button><button class="C7bQRdPs" type="button"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-secondary, currentColor)" title="Unrate 2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#star-outlined"></use></svg></button><button class="C7bQRdPs" type="button"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-secondary, currentColor)" title="Unrate 3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#star-outlined"></use></svg></button><button class="C7bQRdPs" type="button"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-secondary, currentColor)" title="Unrate 4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#star-outlined"></use></svg></button><button class="C7bQRdPs" type="button"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-secondary, currentColor)" title="Unrate 5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#star-outlined"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="b943cnJG "><div class="l0z8Gogx KrByE3IV MWG7WGBE NAlaGptJ JO34GcLR"><div class="NsWdXpRH o8MJIZ9I vmEgUsob"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><div class="ES35fwD6 jA4sXDPG SHv85Oe2 GjgsucRA uedkJzta"><h3 class="_7yoIykb4 OnKOQ4C1 Qu5eWXzk">FAQs</h3></div><h4 class="_7yoIykb4 oddFflBz Qu5eWXzk"></h4></div></div><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><div class="xqKk94yS aVRiZaWa"><button class="A14dw7eb xqKk94yS" type="button"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge gQNAK3AB p38uJJQ1 SHv85Oe2 hTLGYSlU uedkJzta"><span class="_7yoIykb4 PD3FaKoI NDazUVew Qu5eWXzk">What is Envato?</span><div class="XukunOog"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="chevron-down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#chevron-down"></use></svg></div></div></button><div class="XLC7Ta4N"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><span class="_7yoIykb4 Qu5eWXzk"><div>Envato is your one-stop destination for creative assets. With one simple subscription, you can enjoy unlimited downloads of over 24+ million million high-quality assets and templates across the widest range of asset types (cue humble brag). We are always adding new assets daily, but some of our most popular categories include:<br /><ul><li>Audio: <a href="/audio/royalty-free-music">Royalty-Free Music</a>, and <a href="/sound-effects">Sound Effects</a></li><li>Images: <a href="/stock-video">Stock Video</a>, <a href="/video-templates">Video templates</a>, and <a href="/photos">Stock photos</a></li><li>Design: <a href="/graphic-templates">Graphic templates</a>, <a href="/presentation-templates">Presentation templates</a></li><li>And much more!</li></ul></div></span></div></div></div><div class="xqKk94yS aVRiZaWa"><button class="A14dw7eb xqKk94yS" type="button"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge gQNAK3AB p38uJJQ1 SHv85Oe2 hTLGYSlU uedkJzta"><span class="_7yoIykb4 PD3FaKoI NDazUVew Qu5eWXzk">Does Envato sell Fonts?</span><div class="XukunOog"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="chevron-down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#chevron-down"></use></svg></div></div></button><div class="XLC7Ta4N"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><span class="_7yoIykb4 Qu5eWXzk"><div>Envato does not sell individual fonts, with a single subscription you can download any asset across the 24+ million in our library.<br />However, per our <a href="https://help.elements.envato.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000629006-Envato-Elements-User-Terms">User Terms</a> and <a href="https://help.elements.envato.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000621743-Fair-Use-Policy">Fair Use Policy</a>, please remember:<ul><li>The subscription is for an individual (or a specific number of people with our Team or Enterprise accounts).</li><li>No robots allowed. So that means no sharing of accounts or use of automated tools to scrape and download items.</li></ul></div></span></div></div></div><div class="xqKk94yS aVRiZaWa"><button class="A14dw7eb xqKk94yS" type="button"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge gQNAK3AB p38uJJQ1 SHv85Oe2 hTLGYSlU uedkJzta"><span class="_7yoIykb4 PD3FaKoI NDazUVew Qu5eWXzk">How does licensing work for Fonts?</span><div class="XukunOog"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="chevron-down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#chevron-down"></use></svg></div></div></button><div class="XLC7Ta4N"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><span class="_7yoIykb4 Qu5eWXzk"><div>Fonts are covered under the Envato 'Tools License' — a single-use license per device/subscription. It allows broad commercial usage for any logo or design you create during your active subscription. Once created, your commercial rights to these works continue permanently, even after subscription cancellation.</div></span></div></div></div><div class="xqKk94yS aVRiZaWa"><button class="A14dw7eb xqKk94yS" type="button"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge gQNAK3AB p38uJJQ1 SHv85Oe2 hTLGYSlU uedkJzta"><span class="_7yoIykb4 PD3FaKoI NDazUVew Qu5eWXzk">What formats are included in these fonts?</span><div class="XukunOog"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="chevron-down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#chevron-down"></use></svg></div></div></button><div class="XLC7Ta4N"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><span class="_7yoIykb4 Qu5eWXzk"><div>Fonts on Envato typically come in OpenType (.OTF) or TrueType (.TTF) format, and include at minimum uppercase, lowercase letters and numerals. Many also offer expanded or extended character sets (accents, symbols, glyphs) to support broader design needs. In these formats you can also find <a href="/fonts/decorative">decorative fonts</a>, and <a href="/fonts/serif">Serif fonts</a>.</div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ds-color-scheme-light ds-b1394hzq"></div><!--/$--></main><div class="ES35fwD6 LBfqNhja l38mXzx2"><div class="ES35fwD6 Z8wCehge sNjFhu89"><div class="UBgzrYuy FKVlyqqM"><div class="FKVlyqqM Aj9n55u7"><footer class="ES35fwD6"><div class="ES35fwD6 YM4nNcdm ND_FUHoh uVWiYOQK SHv85Oe2 ZxRWRsPP R9RtEYxp OLqHcy86 uedkJzta" data-testid="footer-standard"><div class="QejAgNG_ X10Zn1Lf"><div class="l0z8Gogx KrByE3IV X10Zn1Lf IvjPWeCx"><div class="Q8uZoYoE" data-testid="footer-marketing-panel"><div class="NsWdXpRH o8MJIZ9I vjNqqz_P"><div class="QejAgNG_ rGep5HSU"><a class="XnPoMwM8" href="https://elements.envato.com/"><div class="ES35fwD6 hpXGB4LP Z8wCehge ZAaTEPZZ" data-testid="envato-logo"><img src="https://assets.elements.envato.com/apps/storefront/EnvatoLogoDark-d7fdce89d7315fa71e83.svg" height="32" width="140" alt="Envato"/></div></a><div class="dlqG_UTL"><div class="LTyNgPJu gktLxQxk exzsVg0t i7W3a7Tu"><a title="Envato - Instagram" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/envato/"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="instagram" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#instagram"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - TikTok" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@envato"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="tik-tok" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#tik-tok"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - Facebook" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/envato/"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="facebook-square" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#facebook-square"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - YouTube" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/Envato"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="youtube-outlined" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#youtube-outlined"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - Reddit" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/envato/"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="reddit" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#reddit"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - Pinterest" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.pinterest.com.au/envato"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="pinterest" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#pinterest"></use></svg></div></a><a title="Envato - Twitter" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://x.com/envato"><div class="tP7ovkfG"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="twitter-x" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#twitter-x"></use></svg></div></a></div></div><div class="ES35fwD6 C8LHFU6K SHv85Oe2 GjgsucRA uedkJzta" data-testid="footer-mailing-list"><div class="QejAgNG_ gktLxQxk"><span class="_7yoIykb4 oddFflBz Qu5eWXzk"><strong>Yes to creative inspo in your inbox.</strong> <!-- -->Fresh tutorials, trends, tools (and no boring bits).</span><form method="post"><div class="FRNkUjB9"><div class="Lb1Msz5Y"><span class="_7yoIykb4 oddFflBz Qu5eWXzk"><input type="text" class="gWDTsrqz" aria-label="Sign me up" placeholder="Your email" data-testid="footer-mailing-list-field" value=""/></span></div><button class="ZOiPIr1R" aria-label="Sign me up" data-testid="footer-mailing-list-button" type="submit"><svg class="ovfKxhpl CiKgWgb0" style="--color:var(--color-content-primary, currentColor)" title="Sign me up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img"><use href="#send"></use></svg></button></div></form><span class="_7yoIykb4 DbkD6_G1 hfldU1gb">Unsubscribe any time.<!-- --> <a class="MwuuClIh REJFlh_K" href="https://www.envato.com/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ES35fwD6 Z8wCehge XVtoiESc bjEsgNWZ M7ikmWSE l38mXzx2"><div class="SiHFwTTa" data-testid="footer-links-panel"><div class="QejAgNG_ akbOyW7N"><span class="_7yoIykb4 NDazUVew Qu5eWXzk">Discover</span><span class="_7yoIykb4 oddFflBz Qu5eWXzk"><a class="MwuuClIh GbsYiegj" href="https://elements.e